        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Clean Slate through Repayment Act of </b><strong>2022</strong></p> <p>This bill provides for the removal of any adverse credit history related to a defaulted federal student loan from a borrower's credit history once the borrower has repaid in full the amount due on the loan.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
