      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend the Higher Education Act of 1965 to remove the record of default on a loan made, insured, or guaranteed under title IV from a borrower's credit history upon repayment of the full amount due on such loan.</title>
